## 四、树状结构优化

### 4.1 连接线结构

**目标**：
- 同辈之间不需要横向连接线
- 夫妻节点与每个子女之间有纵向连接线
- 每层之间用虚线分隔不同辈分

### 4.2 CSS 结构

```css
/* 同辈之间无连接线 - 移除了 .children-nodes::before */

/* 每层辈分虚线 */
.children-wrapper {
  padding-top: 40px;
}

.children-wrapper::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  height: 2px;
  background: repeating-linear-gradient(
    90deg,
    #667eea 0,
    #667eea 8px,
    transparent 8px,
    transparent 16px
  );
  opacity: 0.5;
}

/* 每个子节点的独立纵向连接线 */
.child-branch {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  position: relative;
}

.child-branch::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 50%;
  width: 2px;
  height: 40px;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
  transform: translateX(-50%);
}
```

**文件**：`frontend/src/views/genealogy/components/GenealogyNode.vue`

